        "hidden_state_type": "hidden_automation",
        "description": "Automation state — Logic's track automation and region automation curves, their parameter targets, and per-track mode (Read/Touch/Latch/Write) — is not available from exported stems unless separately documented.",
        "consequence": "Temporal mix decisions such as vocal rides, send throws, or filter sweeps may be audible as a printed gain or timbre envelope, but the point-by-point curves and their targets are no longer editable DAW state.",
